28:06.152 --> 28:07.820
I knew it had to be
work-related.

28:07.920 --> 28:10.156
And my guess is, it has
something to do with drugs?

28:10.256 --> 28:12.925
See? My wife.
And a damn good cop.

28:13.025 --> 28:15.061
Yeah. Now she has to leave.

28:15.161 --> 28:17.830
Even though I have an idea
how to get to the bottom of it?

28:17.930 --> 28:20.132
Let me help out,
I'll tell you what it is.

28:22.902 --> 28:24.937
WOMAN (over P.A.):
Dr. Patel to Radiology.

28:25.037 --> 28:26.538
Dr. Patel
