28:26.638 --> 28:29.175
Ms. Duckworth,
we understand

28:29.275 --> 28:30.676
your husband came
out of his coma?

28:30.777 --> 28:32.044
He did.
He's gonna be okay.

28:32.144 --> 28:35.047
Great.
I was just
calling my kids.

28:39.251 --> 28:40.452
Mr. Duckworth,

28:40.552 --> 28:42.789
I'm Detective Reagan,
my partner Detective Baez.

28:42.889 --> 28:44.356
We've been working
your case.

28:44.456 --> 28:45.892
