a couple of shows.

29:13.085 --> 29:15.788
Of course I'm the one paying for
the tickets, the crappy hotel.

29:15.888 --> 29:17.389
I only went out that night
to find a market

29:17.489 --> 29:20.659
'cause the room service
prices were so outrageous.

29:20.759 --> 29:22.494
So you went out,
you got attacked.

29:22.594 --> 29:24.063
Did this guy say anything?

29:24.163 --> 29:27.333
No, he-he just bumped into me,
so I say, "Excuse me,"

29:27.433 --> 29:30.069
