like totally nuts.

29:30.169 --> 29:32.171
When you say he was a kid...?

29:32.271 --> 29:33.906
College-aged.

29:34.006 --> 29:35.374
His pals called him Spencer,

29:35.474 --> 29:37.676
and they must have been
in a frat 'cause I saw

29:37.776 --> 29:39.678
Greek letters
tattooed on his hand.

29:39.778 --> 29:41.881
A white frat boy
named Spencer...

29:41.981 --> 29:44.650
The last place
we were looking.

29:48.387 --> 29:50.089
So, Sandi,
you lied to Tracy

29:50.189 --> 29:51.490
when you told her
that you were quitting

29:51.590 --> 29:52.892
