30:31.763 --> 30:33.165
Ten-hut!

30:41.440 --> 30:44.010
Sorry for the interruption, Sergeant.

30:44.110 --> 30:45.411
Sir.

30:45.511 --> 30:46.879
Thank you.

30:48.447 --> 30:49.882
