31:07.666 --> 31:09.501
So let's have 'em.

31:09.601 --> 31:10.903
Well, I think
she's doing a terrific job...

31:11.003 --> 31:12.738
All right, one at a time, please.

31:13.672 --> 31:14.573
Officer...?

31:14.673 --> 31:15.908
Justin, sir.

31:16.008 --> 31:19.745
Officer Justin, and speak up.

31:21.948 --> 31:24.316
Sir, the fact that she's
out on patrol right now

31:24.416 --> 31:25.484
is a joke.

31:25.584 --> 31:26.986
How? By being a great cop?

31:27.086 --> 31:28.454
'Cause that's the only thing
that matters.

31:28.554 --> 31:30.656
Yeah, Commissioner,
he doesn't speak for me.

31:30.756 --> 31:34.026
I've done a million tours with
Gillson, and she's top-notch.

31:34.126 --> 31:36.462
Yeah, but now the public's
gonna be making eyes at her

31:36.562 --> 31:38.464
