31:44.703 --> 31:45.871
Come on!

31:45.972 --> 31:47.006
How long till all this
blows over?

31:47.106 --> 31:48.107
A day?
If it ever blows over...

31:49.575 --> 31:50.676
All right.

31:53.612 --> 31:56.115
Uh, Officer Martinez...

31:57.116 --> 32:00.419
Officer Martinez, you were...

32:00.519 --> 32:03.455
