Excuse me, can we get

36:34.360 --> 36:35.927
three flaming
vodka shots, please?

36:36.027 --> 36:37.729
Actually, we have
a lot to celebrate.

36:37.829 --> 36:39.298
Can you make those
doubles, please?

36:39.398 --> 36:40.599
Ooh!

36:40.699 --> 36:42.468
Now we need to talk
about your taste in men.

36:44.970 --> 36:46.505
Yeah, not great.

