It's not great.
Whatever, it's not,
it's not great.

36:47.906 --> 36:49.375
It's not great, right?

36:57.583 --> 36:59.585
Hi.
Jack.

36:59.685 --> 37:01.119
Congratulations.

37:01.219 --> 37:03.489
I heard that, uh, Holly Davis
dropped her lawsuit,

37:03.589 --> 37:07.293
and I knew that that wasn't
because you followed my advice.

37:08.360 --> 37:11.297
I can't do things
the way you do.

37:12.731 --> 37:14.232
At least Anthony can't gloat

37:14.333 --> 37:16.034
'cause I know that you didn't
take his advice either.

37:16.134 --> 37:18.937
He meant well,
