Please.

39:07.713 --> 39:09.314
Commissioner.

39:12.751 --> 39:14.185
Have a seat.

39:21.292 --> 39:23.495
Thanks for coming up.

39:23.595 --> 39:24.730
Of course.

39:24.830 --> 39:26.998
Beat me to the punch,
