39:28.366 --> 39:30.969
That's not how I wanted
this to go.

39:31.069 --> 39:33.505
Only way it can.

39:34.773 --> 39:36.542
Look...

39:36.642 --> 39:40.211
I know firsthand how brutal
the papers can be

39:40.311 --> 39:45.050
to anyone on the job, but...

39:46.151 --> 39:49.721
It's not that... sir.

39:49.821 --> 39:51.890
Then what?

39:51.990 --> 39:53.224
I mean, yeah.

39:54.192 --> 39:55.561
It's no fun seeing my name

39:55.661 --> 39:57.796
and my photos splashed everywhere.

40:00.298 --> 40:01.467
But when news got out,

40:01.567 --> 40:04.736
my followers went
through the roof.

40:06.237 --> 40:08.940
Doubled, tripled...

40:09.040 --> 40:11.009
still counting.

40:15.013 --> 40:17.348
And with it, their donations.

40:18.216 --> 40:20.686
In amounts that
I can't turn down.

40:42.073 --> 40:44.309
You can put that back on.

40:51.883 --> 40:54.152
I can't give up the side gig.

40:56.755 --> 40:59.925
I have 35,000 cops
under my command.

41:00.025 --> 41:03.261
What they do on their own time
is none of my business

41:03.361 --> 41:06.565
unless they're breaking the law,
which you are not.

41:07.533 --> 41:10.201
So you're forbidding me to quit?

41:10.969 --> 41:12.370
I am.

41:13.972 --> 41:18.076
I can't afford to lose any cops,
let alone an exceptional one.

41:33.692 --> 41:35.226
Thank you, sir.

41:36.995 --> 41:38.329
And if...

41:38.429 --> 41:43.001
anyone comes at you
with this personal stuff,

41:43.101 --> 41:45.403
let your partner handle it.

41:45.503 --> 41:48.173
Save your adrenaline
for the folks who need you.

41:48.273 --> 41:50.441
Copy that, sir.

41:52.477 --> 41:53.712
And...

41:54.913 --> 41:57.849
...maybe could we...

